title: Coronavirus: Varadkar 'confident' about lifting Irish lockdown

maintext: "Whilst every death is of concern, in the last seven days we've seen the lowest daily number of deaths and cases since March," he said, adding that four guiding principles will be followed going forward - "isolate, test, trace and treat".
